places.name: Mkhaya Game Reserve
places.perex: Mkhaya Game Reserve is a protected area in Swaziland. It is located along the MR8 road.

places.name: Maguga Dam
places.perex: The Maguga Dam is a dam on the Komati River in Swaziland. It is 115 metres high and is located about 12 kilometres south of Piggs Peak.

places.name: Galería de Indingilizi
places.perex: La Galería de Indingilizi es una galería de arte en la ciudad de Mbabane, en el país africano de Suazilandia, establecido en 1982.
